{
  "_comment": "Cross-implementation golden vectors. app (vitest) and firmware (native Unity) MUST both pass these. 'expectedLinear' is renderCue() output BEFORE masterBrightness and BEFORE gamma. Rounding is round-half-up, clamp [0,255].",

